{"tid":1787351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共搞左咁多年紅色娛樂圈，唔比人搞黃色經濟圈咁好笑","createTime":"2019-12-18T00:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T14:22:27.000Z","uid":72431,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f635f502b568c6d41b688d5648ac47864f096ef","tid":1787351,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T00:59:34.000Z","msg":"唔做護旗手就無得撈/封殺<br />\n<br />\n咪一鳩樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7448c847f1ec741e054466c84b5a5a3cf16417","tid":1787351,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:02:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d9d9a3848c4ec22fa3f461099bf1751c702dc55","tid":1787351,"uid":44510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71d400908ab09ec2575a8ba6e3eb3edb5cfedce6","tid":1787351,"uid":126889,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"跟本佢閙你乜 佢自己做過哂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一言不合打人》支那人性格<br />\n白色恐怖 炒人要脅生計》共匪拿手好戲<br />\n文革人民鬥人民》有眼睇<br />\n破壞經濟》讀過中史就知共匪竊國後點破壞<br />\n美化暴力》用文明、法治等概念不停洗腦 佢暴力得你唔得<br />\n洗腦》唔洗講佢地係宗師<br />\n私刑》就算冇今次運動 警察不嬲係警局私刑人是常識吧<br />\n<br />\n可惜有大班人不停去用返上面堆野去質疑自己友"},{"pid":"1a377775ff445abb34f1514d1864b56de8ff6595","tid":1787351,"uid":7343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"黑社會話人黑社會"},{"pid":"5b8da9a0e1c6c2a45fa0d04de3e2cb3c5a3199fe","tid":1787351,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d400908ab09ec2575a8ba6e3eb3edb5cfedce6","tid":1787351,"uid":126889,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"跟本佢閙你乜 佢自己做過哂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一言不合打人》支那人性格<br />\n白色恐怖 炒人要脅生計》共匪拿手好戲<br />\n文革人民鬥人民》有眼睇<br />\n破壞經濟》讀過中史就知共匪竊國後點破壞<br />\n美化暴力》用文明、法治等概念不停洗腦 佢暴力得你唔得<br />\n洗腦》唔洗講佢地係宗師<br />\n私刑》就算冇今次運動 警察不嬲係警局私刑人是常識吧<br />\n<br />\n可惜有大班人不停去用返上面堆野去質疑自己友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"外國勢力》俄共支援中共"},{"pid":"05fd9b3b25c8209fd7701fe403763272103d9fb0","tid":1787351,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaa7d8f8394cec5a1fdc1f6ee31583d3b651076","tid":1787351,"uid":304726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:33:57.000Z","msg":"老老實實，太天真同幼稚嘅人先會在乎敵人意見，大家手足有腦識諗，邊樣做得邊做唔樣得大家心中有數啦，洗乜理敵人講乜，對家同你講搞嚟冇用就當晒真，咁係咪坐起到就抗爭到？做順民咁就唔洗反啦，咩都唔做敵人咪最開心囉。你會唔會見美國啲議員比中共爽仔話幾句就唔通過人權法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗乜對家屈你係港獨就怕？我覺得幾時都由佢地屈，根本我地做乜都會比佢地屈港獨，我地反而唔洗講出口，由佢地幫我地做宣傳，等大家市民聽慣咗習以為常個時，假港獨都變真港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係話大家唔需要有大局觀，但大局觀係為咗顧全大局、應對敵人、為自己尋求最優解，並唔係順應敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc70a998850214ad2f7722f9b1a2b91041adcf64","tid":1787351,"uid":45910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:36:59.000Z","msg":"無停過<br />\n你估食環會唔會搞鳩黃店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de022a62039b0f2c7ed74f31f9dc0896cd7ec151","tid":1787351,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:38:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪中共特色囉佢做就得你就唔得"},{"pid":"121de55eb5d9b30bc4f680b2e3f20c422afca47d","ti